# LocalHub project core

- Read `AGENTS.md` before any implementation.
- Treat `/docs` as the approved project specification.
- Implement the Vue 3 frontend only unless the request explicitly includes backend work.
- The approved MVP is Home, Post CRUD, password-protected edit/delete, post search, map visualization, chatbot, responsive states and deployment readiness.
- Do not implement any Won't-Have item from `docs/01_PRODUCT_REQUIREMENTS.md`.
- Do not infer `TARGET_REGION`, production API URL or map tile provider when marked TBD.
- Explain contract conflicts or missing values before inventing behavior.
